        <a href="/rates/usd-pkr-today/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">💵 USD to PKR Live Rate</a>
        <a href="/guides/roshan-digital-account-guide-usa/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">🏦 Roshan Digital Account Guide</a>
        <a href="/guides/fbar-guide-us-pakistanis/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">📋 FBAR Guide for US Pakistanis</a>
        <a href="/guides/nrp-tax-filer-guide-pakistan/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">📄 NRP Tax Filer Guide</a>
        <a href="/tools/currency-converter/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">💱 Currency Converter</a>
